Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多數異界體正從西南方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計再三十分鐘抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是群體行動的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒帶頭的就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集群防禦系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一、第二靈智型部隊在西南方島嶼迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三、第四、第五部隊在本島西南沿岸佈下防線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:02:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓那些來自宇宙的鼠輩見識一下人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以見識到人類軍的本事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是他們連所羅門系統都還不會使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旺茲是位優秀的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不會這麼輕易敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會祈禱他們不要重蹈摩達維亞的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在CDC是人類軍的指揮總部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳去那裡又能做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連系統都不會用的人 我怎麼能信賴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想以這種方式跟妳重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛耶 你要做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳先待在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳能夠活在世界上的某處 就是我唯一上戰場的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為我走太慢才害妳跟不上大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 不過妳不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我才剛到外面來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不太適應怎麼走路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就邊休息邊走吧 不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳願意聽我一個請求嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 要我揹妳都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望妳可以當我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我連一個朋友都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的朋友不就在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 小芹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有自我介紹過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是避難所的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小芹就跟大家在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城不就是總士學長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說定囉 我們要當朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友 - 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一波動屏障被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人沒有變更前進路線 正筆直往這裡前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直線前進嗎 竟敢瞧不起我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 已經取得外出許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個意思 我是為了比較虛弱的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種時候人類彼此卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴 妳在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情要麻煩當初把我放到系統裡面的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生至今第一次來到外界 所以我還不太會走路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請妳拿一個可以載我移動的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二波動屏障被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校也卯足全力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說對吧 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也比平常還有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛剛去見我以前的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神劍型法夫那要出馬囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西南方登陸 自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是昂宿型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Triple SIX 前往支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農 帶第三部隊繞到左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要夾擊它們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險 在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 連無線通訊都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 Mark III！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機體表面跟皮膚的觸感同步的程度居然這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體好沈重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是神劍型的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快和它同化並接受變性意識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳 站起來打 不然會沒命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城…乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次這樣跟妳說話呢 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨蛇級潛水艦被擊中 三艘都被擊沈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的首領呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知另外的兩艘潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對西南部沿岸進行密集攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己人也一起打？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有生以來第一次玩泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 只是表面燒掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要選擇是從現在才開始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西方出現了第三群
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這座島的西南部份切離 用系統讓它自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把登陸的敵人和島嶼一起炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎擊系統自行運作 拒絕我們的手動控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會動？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰在操縱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法查明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃飯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總部、總部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮系統似乎被截斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情勢正有所變化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉讓我們離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？這是誰幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來好像是想要引導我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妳嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新建立防線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能動的傢伙通通到前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量的昂宿型異界體在龍宮山頂集結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我們正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是島的痛楚傳到我身上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一妳有什麼三長兩短…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我躲起來的話 這座島一定會沉沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前 我必須讓大家做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍骨區塊 (Keel Block)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是兀爾德之泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是強迫要接受的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要以自己的意志重新選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別發呆了 快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要駕駛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不穿作用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎也曾經沒換裝就駕駛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何況…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在不戰鬥就對不起我爸跟甲洋他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的工作是給予大家想要得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓大家再做一次選擇 確定所要的究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這對異界體也是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要請它們做選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此我才會誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴回去吧 避難所還很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳陪我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為系統的研究員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 身為島上的居民我要親眼見證一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被引導來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞瑟王之室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第二CDC嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本構造跟CDC一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認所有系統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把龍宮島的主控權拿回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是這座島 這座島就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在島上的人們想將島變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些人們的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們實際上在追求什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓人們得以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做的只有請他們做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓人們得以理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當初我沒能讓妳做出選擇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也選擇過囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有自我 這就是我的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前有117隻登陸 敵方勢力更加擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昂宿型會發現這裡只是時間上的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二防衛系統呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在執行中 再兩分鐘完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,群體中誕生的主體將索敵系統無效化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法發現本體！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拿法夫那當誘餌 引誘出敵人的首領嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很難 但我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門有反應了 是敵人首領
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將所有迎擊系統集中起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲的來源在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龍宮島西邊的燈塔 我把影像顯示在螢幕上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也要讓異界體選擇嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人本體開始朝燈塔移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有法夫那散開 立刻往島的西邊移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避開敵人前往指示的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要攻擊敵人的本體！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什麼敵人我都會打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕、好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝吧 高拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的動作…是駕駛員換人了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農 找到敵方首領了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們往西邊移動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還可以動的也跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海底飛彈準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark V以神盾系統阻止敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark VIII繞到右側
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark III確認敵方核心並且將其破壞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊 劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准去 維持陣型！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來不及了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連神劍型也抵擋不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標再度朝燈塔移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城乙姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 你們也選好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有對話的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都會消失的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虛無的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做選擇的並不是只有你們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬 我們逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼機體？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擋下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 會被炸掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的核心正從內部被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒被同化了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標又開始消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門的反應消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要尋找就找得到喔 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振動、各種波形、溫度、電子、電波、空間相位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架機體攻擊之後所留下來的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員 你聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的位置捕捉到了 幫忙打倒那傢伙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一…騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要跟系統同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該能跟Mark XI那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你還在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你曾經說過只有這座島是唯一的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當初我不懂這句話的含意 也不知道你在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是聽你的話去戰鬥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在我覺得有點懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實你一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我們一無所知的時候 你就想要保護這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是翔子還有甲洋那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也獨自背負著痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架機體的識別代號是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark Zein
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟系統同步必須登錄機體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我五秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登錄完畢 開始同步處理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得見我看到的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個武器是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是Mark VIII的44機關砲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路迦之槍嗎！
